<i>noun</i>: 치하 [치ː하], 취미 [취ː미], 중시 [중ː시], 절상 [절쌍], 음미 [음미], 사의 [사ː의/사ː이], 고마움 [고ː마움], 감상 [감상], 감사 [감ː사] <br>
<ul>
<li><i>noun</i><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>치하 [치ː하]</dt><br>
<dd>praise; appreciation; compliment</dd><br>
<dd>고마움이나 칭찬의 뜻을 겉으로 드러냄.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of expressing one's gratitude or praising someone.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>취미 [취ː미]</dt><br>
<dd>1. hobby</dd><br>
<dd>좋아하여 재미로 즐겨서 하는 일.</dd><br>
<dd>Something one likes and enjoys doing for fun.</dd><br>
<dd>2. taste; appreciation</dd><br>
<dd>음악이나 미술과 같이 아름다운 것을 감상하고 이해하는 능력.</dd><br>
<dd>An ability to appreciate and understand something beautiful such as music or art.</dd><br>
<dd>3. interest</dd><br>
<dd>흥미를 느끼어 마음이 끌리는 상태.</dd><br>
<dd>The state of feeling interested and being attracted.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>중시 [중ː시]</dt><br>
<dd>valuing; appreciation</dd><br>
<dd>매우 크고 중요하게 여김.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of thinking of something as very significant and important.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>절상 [절쌍]</dt><br>
<dd>appreciation</dd><br>
<dd>화폐 가치를 높임.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of raising the value of a currency.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>음미 [음미]</dt><br>
<dd>1. savoring; enjoying</dd><br>
<dd>시가를 낮은 목소리로 읽거나 외면서 감상함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of appreciating a poem or song, by reading or reciting it quietly.</dd><br>
<dd>2. appreciation</dd><br>
<dd>사물이나 개념의 속 내용을 느끼거나 생각함.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of feeling or thinking about the deeper meaning of an object or a concept.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>사의 [사ː의/사ː이]</dt><br>
<dd>gratitude; appreciation</dd><br>
<dd>감사하게 여기는 마음이나 뜻.</dd><br>
<dd>A thankful mind or an intention of showing thankfulness.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>고마움 [고ː마움]</dt><br>
<dd>thanks; appreciation; gratitude</dd><br>
<dd>남이 자신을 위해 무엇을 해주어서 남에게 보답하고 싶은 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>A desire to repay a favor one has received from others.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>감상 [감상]</dt><br>
<dd>appreciation</dd><br>
<dd>예술 작품이나 경치 등을 즐기고 이해하면서 평가함.</dd><br>
<dd>The act of enjoying, understanding, and assessing a piece of art or scenery.</dd><br>
<dt><span>&#8227;&nbsp;</span>감사 [감ː사]</dt><br>
<dd>gratitude; appreciation; thanks</dd><br>
<dd>고맙게 여김. 또는 그런 마음.</dd><br>
<dd>An act of feeling thankful for something, or such a mind.</dd><br>
</li>
</ul>